{"tid":1272390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 七一遊行（三）：話人係鬼係暴徒之前，你有無見過絕望嘅人係點？","createTime":"2019-07-01T10:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:18:35.000Z","uid":78769,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57b861b33a1721fc2d7d8605665745be6e6767eb","tid":1272390,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"&quot;有兩段對話係值得一記，一段係當鄺俊宇同某位抗爭者嘈交，鬧佢地「就算衝擊無錯，而家並唔係時候」之時，有位抗爭者大聲反駁：「今日唔X衝點對得住班死者？」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;我見好多人響網上嘲笑佢地呢個時候衝擊立法會無用無意義，又話一衝入去等如束手就擒係白痴。但呢班人響最前線衝擊，肯定係最清楚現場風險嘅人，難道一眾網上軍師會比佢地更加清楚？唯一解釋，就係呢班人根本預咗比人拉比人打，有去無回，換言之，係一種另類自殺。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%89-%E8%A9%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E9%AC%BC%E4%BF%82%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E5%98%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E9%BB%9E-f73cf2fa87fd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40henryporterbabe%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%2589-%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%2598%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%25BB%259E-f73cf2fa87fd&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=82d5e565\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%89-%E8%A9%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E9%AC%BC%E4%BF%82%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E5%98%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E9%BB%9E-f73cf2fa87fd</a>"},{"pid":"808e3ee35cff230c33fcbf05ef99f97bc0541186","tid":1272390,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk